ninja.params

Annotation Type WithArgumentExtractors


  • @Target(value=ANNOTATION_TYPE)
 @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
public @interface WithArgumentExtractors
    Indicates that this annotation should use the given argument extractors Allows to specify more than one argument extractor, see WithArgumentExtractor
    Author:
    Christian Bourgeois
